    <article class="article">
      <header class="article-header">
        <h1 title="Can I sort the Novels Rankings by language?" class="article-title">
          Can I sort the Novels Rankings by language?
          
        </h1>

        
      </header>

      <section class="article-info">
        <div class="article-content">
          <div class="article-body"><p><span>You can sort <a href="https://www.pixiv.net/novel/ranking.php?mode=daily" target="_blank" rel="noopener">the Novels Rankings page</a> by language.<br><br>▶<a href="#h_01FKWPMZPB35YQBQ3JSKYEW7Y1" target="_self">On desktop</a><br>▶<a href="#h_01FKWPNS8PTPS5BM0V6AR9T798" target="_self">On mobile</a><br>▶<a href="#h_01FKWPP243ZM8S7A58WN9XCCBY" target="_self">On the app</a></span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3 id="h_01FKWPMZPB35YQBQ3JSKYEW7Y1"><span>On desktop</span></h3>
<ol>
<li><span>Click the language selection menu on <a href="https://www.pixiv.net/novel/ranking.php?mode=daily" target="_blank" rel="noopener">the Novels Ranking page</a>.<a href="/hc/article_attachments/4408919883545/______________.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="/hc/article_attachments/4408919883545/______________.png" alt="______________.png"></a></span></li>
<li><span>Clicking the language you want to display from the pulldown menu will sort the results by the language you specify.<br>* If there aren't any ranked works for the language you select, no works will be displayed.<a href="/hc/article_attachments/4408919917081/_________________.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="/hc/article_attachments/4408919917081/_________________.png" alt="_________________.png" width="313" height="320"></a></span></li>
</ol>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3 id="h_01FKWPNS8PTPS5BM0V6AR9T798"><span>On mobile</span></h3>
<ol>
<li><span>Tap the Ranking options menu on <a href="https://www.pixiv.net/novel/ranking.php?mode=daily" target="_blank" rel="noopener">the Novels Ranking page</a>.<a href="/hc/article_attachments/4408935286681/____________.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="/hc/article_attachments/4408935286681/____________.png" alt="____________.png" width="545" height="244"></a></span></li>
<li><span>Tap "Work language" in Ranking options.</span></li>
<li><span>Tap the language you want to display from the pulldown menu.<img src="/hc/article_attachments/4408928077209/______________.png" alt="______________.png" width="480" height="391"></span></li>
<li><span>Tapping "Apply" will sort the results by the language you specify.<img src="/hc/article_attachments/4409111586073/Screenshot_2021-11-08-16-13-16-05.png" alt="Screenshot_2021-11-08-16-13-16-05.png" width="501" height="478"><br>* If there aren't any ranked works for the language you select, no works will be displayed.</span></li>
</ol>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3 id="h_01FKWPP243ZM8S7A58WN9XCCBY"><span>On the app</span></h3>
<p><span>Currently, you cannot display Rankings by language on the app version of pixiv.</span></p></div>

          <div class="article-attachments">
            <ul class="attachments">
              
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

